{"tid":1717890,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[救你一命]所有人入一入黎","createTime":"2019-11-13T17:06:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T18:36:33.000Z","uid":128413,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"8f5a31e8f1ea9b6b6928685d3046f88ed292ae44","tid":1717890,"uid":128413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T17:06:06.000Z","msg":"今晚又有人墮樓受傷不治<br />\n未肯定前因係咩<br />\n<br />\n但係希望你地所有人都唔好再做獨行俠<br />\n揾多一個人先出去<br />\n<br />\n或者聯絡定親人朋友 你會去邊到<br />\n<br />\n仲有就係 係手機set sos功能 有咩事就用呢個功能佢可以幫你send你嘅訊息俾你嘅家人朋友 有助求救<br />\n<br />\n同埋 盡量減少夜晚係偏遠地區獨行 <br />\n<br />\n唔想再有一位手足死得不明不白<br />\n<br />\n推上熱門 提醒手足"},{"pid":"7a84646993a5b65337fbc92df156f21e28914837","tid":1717890,"uid":144849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T17:06:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"31cc8ae81db048d6010f94e8b8e97ef2598b1357","tid":1717890,"uid":89006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T17:06:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7a854ca653821463bd3da5f14bb47cbadf30115a","tid":1717890,"uid":326463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T17:07:02.000Z","msg":"11.14 曙光行動 繼續三罷<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1714238\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1714238</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e5836d83f41ede128d9667bddbf57f7dcc680ed3","tid":1717890,"uid":128413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T17:09:45.000Z","msg":"勿獨行"},{"pid":"78c8d0e7bcfb275c0a0a01a51b086e18a88b2a7b","tid":1717890,"uid":82588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T17:09:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6650b608648c2de054c0a8296fdc5cee58587709","tid":1717890,"uid":128413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T17:13:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e554feeb123fe786370243014673536a7abb217d","tid":1717890,"uid":128413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T17:54:47.000Z","msg":"推呀 幫手啦"},{"pid":"e8792bdaa7c2c9d78379e6881d